{"tid":1696732,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[真本土港產片] 《獅子山上》入唔入場支持？","createTime":"2019-11-06T10:46:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T20:15:34.000Z","uid":15213,"like":64,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"d2ad7ec5dc3ac6ec579cb0c260f15068aaad0022","tid":1696732,"uid":15213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T10:46:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">《獅子山上》LION ROCK </span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/mdP4PPS.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y2BDtCi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY2BDtCi.jpg&h=d6163ad3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n導演：梁國斌<br />\n演員：林德信、衛詩雅、朱鑑然、袁澧林<br />\n<br />\n簡介：<br />\n真人真事改編。世界排名第八的攀石運動員黎志偉，因車禍而半身不遂，生命迎來巨變。怎料，重傷後的志偉發現自己因意外而獲得異能&mdash;從他人身上看到代表其真面目的「動物」！自此，他在動物世界飽覽眾生相，走進一段奇幻復康旅程。從各動物的人生百態中，他逐漸由無法接受事實到放下過去的成就光環，為了所愛的家人和證明自已，他堅持坐著輪椅也要攀上獅子山上，活出新的自己。《死開啲啦》導演梁國斌再次執導，拍出不屈不撓的香港精神。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">上畫日：</span></span><br />\n11月14日 星期四<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本土片一定入場支持<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />港產片不了"},{"pid":"a8ba5364b44f2d56b46b12b7a879153ac7b81afd","tid":1696732,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T10:48:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a49a264f2495420bd2bda22750154130aaeb2446","tid":1696732,"uid":313584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T10:49:20.000Z","msg":"撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e90683373803699247d2b62e35f09bd3381640","tid":1696732,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T11:06:31.000Z","msg":"想睇ufo多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7875d162b9f3f5313415f9f74a58fa0812bee56","t